# Changelog

**6.2.0** (Sep 7, 2019)
  * Expose `Humanize` module, enhancing documentation (thanks @ coinop-logan)

**6.1.0** (Jul 21, 2019)
  * Add `humanize` function

**6.0.2** (Aug 28, 2018)
  * Upgrade to Elm 0.19

**6.0.1** (Jul 12, 2018)
  * Use `elm-round` 1.0.3 (or higher) to fix the bug with too large (or tiny) numbers (usually with scientific notation)

**6.0.0** (May 15, 2018)
  * Add positive prefix/suffix to `Locale`s (thanks @joshhornby)

**5.0.5** (May 15, 2018)
  * Fix test suite

**5.0.4** (May 15, 2018)
  * Update `hoek` dependency due to a vulnerability in older versions of this package
  * Update elm-verify-examples (dependency for development)

**5.0.3** (Feb 23, 2018)
  * Update dependencies & documentation

**5.0.2** (Jul 23, 2017)
  * Update documentation

**5.0.1** (Jul 23, 2017)
  * Update documentation

**5.0.0** (Jul 23, 2017)
  * Support for customization of the negative representation

**4.0.2** (Jun 4, 2017)
  * Update documentation

**4.0.1** (Apr 1, 2017)
  * Fix bug with negative numbers (thanks @pedrocalderon)
  * Fix bug large numbers (thanks @chancyk)

**4.0.0** (Feb 24, 2017)
  * `Locale` now lives inside `FormatNumber` module to avoid conflicts (thanks @peteygao)

**3.0.0** (Feb 11, 2017)
  * No more chance to format `Int`: one `format` to rule them all (thanks @rogeriochaves)
  * Useful `Locale`s included (thanks @lovasoa)
  * Minor fixes

**2.0.0** (Dec 27, 2016)
  * Introduce `Locale` type alias

**1.0.0** (Dec 17, 2016)